title: Prepping for Fantasy Playoffs and Initial Advice After Week 10 | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 343)
description:
Josh Reynolds and Anthony Miller lead this week’s Initial Advice roster (1:00), Rashaad Penny and Lamar Jackson are among the top players to add off waivers this week (18:00), and Malcolm Brown and Austin Ekeler lead the group of signature players to grab while you still can as playoff preparation season has officially commenced (34:30).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
